  </p>

  <h2>3. Definitions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Service</strong>: all Scluba tools (site, web app, iOS/Android apps, recap card).</li>
    <li><strong>Partner club</strong>: golf club that has subscribed to the Scluba offering.</li>
    <li><strong>Player</strong>: natural person using the Service, typically after scanning a QR code at the desk of a Partner club.</li>
    <li><strong>User</strong>: any site visitor or Player using the Service, whether or not they have an account.</li>
    <li><strong>Account</strong>: optional personal area allowing the Player to keep their history.</li>
    <li><strong>Content</strong>: scores, statistics, shareable photos, and any data generated by use of the Service.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Access to the Service</h2>
  <p>
    The Service is freely available to Players scanning a Partner club's QR code, 24/7, subject to
    possible interruptions for maintenance or force majeure.
  </p>
  <p>
